Package: installgithub
Title: Install R Packages from 'GitHub'
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gabor Csardi
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <gcsardi@mango-solutions.com>
Description: Download and install R packages stored in GitHub repositories. This package is a lightweight replacement of `devtools::install_github()`.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/mangothecat/installgithub
BugReports: https://github.com/mangothecat/installgithub/issues
Suggests: 
    testthat
